dct_title_s: Chart prepared by James B. Moore to accompany his memorial to Congress respecting the subject of steam communication with China, Japan & c, 1850.
dct_description_sm: Inset: Harbour of San Francisco, California. Tables of distances. Shows distances between major ports of the world. 1 map; 71 x 96 cm.
